}[/code] one more thing to add to the top of the command
see the 9, and the 9 in the second line, amount int, we need to edit this number for you command, first u count the letters in the command  B=1 u=2 y=3 e=4 a=5 r=6 t=7 h=8 and then you +1 =9 so you edit the number to 9 - this is mandatory, if u dont edit this the command will lagg u out



